    "artifact_power": "splits any problem into perfect equal parts with one swift strike",
    "greeting": "Pirate, the cherry blossoms are falling — but something's wrong on Hanaydo Island!",
    "act1": "You step onto soft pink petals covering ancient stone paths. Cherry trees tower above you, their branches heavy with fruit. In the distance, a golden temple glows between the trees. The air smells sweet and warm.",
    "act2": "The Monkey-Samurai has stolen all the cherry baskets and locked them inside the temple! He's trying to divide them into his army of monkey warriors — but he keeps getting the math wrong. Now cherries are rolling everywhere, and the temple doors won't open until the baskets are shared equally.",
    "act3": "Only you can solve the division puzzles and open the temple, Pirate. Inside waits the Blade of Light — a legendary sword that can split any problem into perfect equal parts with one swift strike.",
    "goal": "Division is your superpower for sharing things fairly — no one gets left out, and every group gets exactly the same amount."
  },
